<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #eef1f6, #dde7f3);
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .bag-container {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 40px; /* Adds spacing so 404 doesn't hover over text */
        }
        .bag {
            width: 100px;
            height: 80px;
            background: rgb(122, 154, 213);
            border: 2px solid #6ea0d9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
        }
        .bag::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 40px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 3px solid #333;
            border-color: transparent transparent #333 transparent;
            border-radius: 50%;
            top: -12px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        .error-number {
            font-size: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            position: absolute;
            top: -55px; /* Moves 404 close to the bag */
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6 error-container">
                <h3 class="fw-bold text-dark">We lost that page...</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary">
                    The page you are looking for was moved, removed, or might never have existed. Here are some helpful ideas:
                </p>
                <div class="bag-container">
                    <div class="error-number">404</div>
                    <div class="bag"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="input-group mt-3">
                    <span class="input-group-text">üîç</span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="What are you looking for?">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
